","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"I'm running Eclipse 3.7-linux-gtk-x86_64 on Ubuntu 11.04. Whenever I run the\nHiveCli launch configuration from within Eclipse it causes Eclipse to freeze.\n\nI did some debugging and determined that the freeze is triggered by the\ninitialization of the jline ConsoleReader class in CliDriver. More digging\nyielded the interesting fact that this behavior disappears when I remove\nthe -Dhive.root.logger=INFO,console setting from the launch configuration.\n ","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=cwsteinbach","name":"cwsteinbach","key":"cwsteinbach","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Carl Steinbach","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2011-11-29T06:58:50.155+0000","updated":"2011-11-29T06:58:50.155+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12533072/comment/13159133","id":"13159133","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=jiraposter%40reviews.apache.org","name":"jiraposter@reviews.apache.org","key":"jiraposter@reviews.apache.org","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"jiraposter@reviews.apache.org","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"\n-----------------------------------------------------------\nThis is an automatically generated e-mail. To reply, visit:\nhttps://reviews.apache.org/r/2958/\n-----------------------------------------------------------\n\nReview request for hive and John Sichi.\n\n\nSummary\n-------\n\nThis is a fix for HIVE-2613.\n\n* Set the encoding for the console appender in hive-log4j.properties\n* Add hive-log4j.properties to the classpath of the HiveCli launch configuration.\n\n\nThis addresses bug HIVE-2613.\n    https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-2613\n\n\nDiffs\n-----\n\n  common/src/java/conf/hive-log4j.properties 9e2a1cc \n  eclipse-templates/HiveCLI.launchtemplate 40f68ac \n\nDiff: https://reviews.apache.org/r/2958/diff\n\n\nTesting\n-------\n\n\nThanks,\n\nCarl\n\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=jiraposter%40reviews.apache.org","name":"jiraposter@reviews.apache.org","key":"jiraposter@reviews.apache.org","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"jiraposter@reviews.apache.org","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2011-11-29T07:11:39.604+0000","updated":"2011-11-29T07:11:39.604+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12533072/comment/13159555","id":"13159555","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=jvs","name":"jvs","key":"jvs","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"John Sichi","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"body":"+1, will comm